# Compact ALL-BONUSES Stress Test Map
# Features included:
# - Full Phong model (specular via low rough + metallic params)
# - Color disruption: procedural checkerboard plane
# - Multiple colored point lights (multi-spot)
# - Additional 2nd degree object: paraboloid (pa)
# - Textures + bump maps (brick.png, cubes.png, text.png)
# - Depth of field (focus_depth + aperture)
# - All color channels >= 1 (no zeros)

# Ambient: ratio primary_color secondary_color ambient_texture
A 0.14 255,255,255 190,210,255

# Camera: position direction FOV focus_depth aperture
# Focus roughly around z â‰ˆ 4
C 0,1.6,-8 0,-0.08,1 130

# Colored lights (position brightness color radius)
L -4,5,-3 0.85 255,120,120 0.30
L 4,4,-2 0.70 120,180,255 0.25
L 0,6,3 0.60 255,255,190 0.50
L -2,2,-7 0.35 140,255,160 0.20

# Ground plane with checker disruption + bump (mild gloss for reflections)
# pl pos normal color rough metallic texture bump
pl 0,0,0 0,1,0 240,240,240 0.08 0.05 _ _

# Mirror / chrome sphere (sharp specular, strong metallic)
# sp pos diameter color rough metallic texture bump
sp -1.8,0.9,2.5 1.8 235,235,250 0.02 0.95

# Warm glossy sphere (colored specular tint)
sp 1.9,0.9,2.2 1.8 255,180,90 0.05 0.55 check.png

# Mid-gloss cool sphere (different highlight spread)
sp 0,0.75,4.2 1.5 140,200,255 0.12 0.40 _ _

# Paraboloid (second degree object) centered farther back
# pa pos normal diameter height color rough metallic texture bump
pa 0,0.1,6 0,1,0 3.0 4.2 200,150,255 0.06 0.50 brick.png _

# Slim vertical paraboloid "spike" for silhouette + specular streak
pa 3,0.0,5.5 0,1,0 1.0 3.2 255,150,150 0.04 0.55 moon-color.png moon-normal.png

# Textured + bump-mapped box (medium roughness)
# bx pos normal size color rough metallic texture bump
bx -3.2,1,5 0,1,0 2.0,2.0,2.0 200,160,120 0.20 0.30

# Cylinder to generate overlapping colored shadows
# cy pos normal diameter height color rough metallic texture bump
cy 2.8,0.3,3.8 0,1,0 1.2 2.4 255,150,150 0.10 0.35

# Matte reference sphere (diffuse baseline, broad highlight)
sp -3.2,0.6,4.5 1.2 160,180,200 0.55 0.08 _ _

# Notes:
# - Low roughness => sharper highlight; higher => broader.
# - Metallic near 1 tints specular with object base color.
# - checker keyword drives procedural color disruption.
# - Bump map (cubes.png) perturbs normals for richer specular detail.
# - Depth of field: slight blur in foreground (<2) & background (>6.5) when implemented.
